{"tid":1161210,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"周芷若趙敏鬥到去機場　祝緒丹潮味完勝陳鈺琪","createTime":"2019-05-19T04:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T10:39:25.000Z","uid":58335,"like":9,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"b16ae4a43b88513cf5c5c0a71a3ca2abb255a897","tid":1161210,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T04:21:21.000Z","msg":"標題係HK01寫<br />\n唔關我事<br />\n我覺得兩個都咁靚<br />\n好喜歡丹丹琪琪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813546/org/dcd53ff6e742ca51fa64f14b5bfc7dd7.jpg/khSXfRuQmQODBXvtkAmuWdTmTnnu-mgZRvDkxUbw5MU?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813546%2Forg%2Fdcd53ff6e742ca51fa64f14b5bfc7dd7.jpg%2FkhSXfRuQmQODBXvtkAmuWdTmTnnu-mgZRvDkxUbw5MU%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=e0150e90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撰文：董欣琪<br />\n2019-05-19 00:00<br />\n最後更新日期：2019-05-19 00:00<br />\n身為藝人，當然要無時無刻保持最佳狀態。對於女藝人來說，在活動及頒獎禮上爭妍鬥麗已經是再平常不過的事，就連世界各地的機場都成為她們比拼的戰場。最近新版《倚天屠龍記》在翡翠台熱播，劇中一眾女演員包括周海媚、祝緒丹、陳鈺琪、曹曦月等都備受關注，她們的古裝扮相各有特色，但原來她們的機場造型也充滿時尚感，更能看到她們真實的一面。<br />\n<br />\n1. 祝緒丹<br />\n<br />\n由祝緒丹飾演的周芷若獲網民大讚仙氣十足，展現古典美，更被譽為最美周芷若，顏值直逼當年周海媚所飾演的版本。但其實她的時裝打扮都充滿時尚感，機場Look更非常值得參考，上身以T恤襯外套，而下身就選擇黑色牛仔褲，一下就拉長了整個人的線條比例，更顯瘦和高䠷！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813007/org/a2dd47598af103401f8f8b55ac5d5c28.jpeg/AwrOUVz24EZBWZL3yoRfDLsmPFVq3-6gjrj5Lo64-S4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813007%2Forg%2Fa2dd47598af103401f8f8b55ac5d5c28.jpeg%2FAwrOUVz24EZBWZL3yoRfDLsmPFVq3-6gjrj5Lo64-S4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=aa441ba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813030/org/16a6282c6391bf3712a6493754d8a4a6.jpeg/k3e9_9BFbALStdHKOGkshZbs4ilbsKzIxj_g7MY_4Ow\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813030%2Forg%2F16a6282c6391bf3712a6493754d8a4a6.jpeg%2Fk3e9_9BFbALStdHKOGkshZbs4ilbsKzIxj_g7MY_4Ow&h=f114ceef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813023/org/7912a3c269c47b5e00e45cb24840c7fb.jpeg/mtVhhf3M0JVrZq3gS9nHyU-OlK9N3YNaz78XWc-_F1k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813023%2Forg%2F7912a3c269c47b5e00e45cb24840c7fb.jpeg%2FmtVhhf3M0JVrZq3gS9nHyU-OlK9N3YNaz78XWc-_F1k&h=ded2c3dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813031/org/5940ffe29663b1189cab4a2239a7b22a.jpg/tfsiXXw-TMKxMsfAR2aImvZN8md0rM-1q7OtWquzrVo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813031%2Forg%2F5940ffe29663b1189cab4a2239a7b22a.jpg%2FtfsiXXw-TMKxMsfAR2aImvZN8md0rM-1q7OtWquzrVo&h=74c6da94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813018/org/d4df82002264f842a2aaf2036068d2bc.jpeg/glu6ZWJeF6k-jVEmobGxvly9Jf8lmIfCc5OUWXOTlFk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813018%2Forg%2Fd4df82002264f842a2aaf2036068d2bc.jpeg%2Fglu6ZWJeF6k-jVEmobGxvly9Jf8lmIfCc5OUWXOTlFk&h=9b1fc589&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 陳鈺琪<br />\n而飾演趙敏的陳鈺琪也令人眼前一亮，清秀的面容，扮演古裝角色時卻帶着幾分英氣。曾出演過多部古裝劇的她，是唐嫣旗下藝人，她更被外界稱為「唐嫣接班人」。高高瘦瘦的陳鈺琪，機場造型就走型格風，與她在劇中的角色有幾分相似。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813073/org/c4ab20f1c26aa090649a78c65898b5d5.jpg/R_iBUsiBioGhlSZbfT_JgYd54EluRnR1FNtqghTbaoI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813073%2Forg%2Fc4ab20f1c26aa090649a78c65898b5d5.jpg%2FR_iBUsiBioGhlSZbfT_JgYd54EluRnR1FNtqghTbaoI&h=5964667d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813083/org/df3e0a8d940123da3906dda017de6aad.jpg/I92wUymrdrY540AlqBWzvKOSlx1cgseJ3sLrqN7C66g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813083%2Forg%2Fdf3e0a8d940123da3906dda017de6aad.jpg%2FI92wUymrdrY540AlqBWzvKOSlx1cgseJ3sLrqN7C66g&h=5d09906e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813097/org/ea79216206ba5a5ccc9dd2aa82d1d4c5.jpg/Gn0XptyOWA43faCM4Qmshd9o-SS8NUxx0s-0y9LPtMs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813097%2Forg%2Fea79216206ba5a5ccc9dd2aa82d1d4c5.jpg%2FGn0XptyOWA43faCM4Qmshd9o-SS8NUxx0s-0y9LPtMs&h=fccaf579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813089/org/1f526286c4c5017b47a04754b41dce75.jpg/eLe10WADwOOc7WMH3Brwig6Ir1fzHyx2Oi6MdzoujHc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813089%2Forg%2F1f526286c4c5017b47a04754b41dce75.jpg%2FeLe10WADwOOc7WMH3Brwig6Ir1fzHyx2Oi6MdzoujHc&h=83a36279&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813103/org/b2e9571d6001a4647770091fc6cd6d4a.jpeg/08VQczKJBgQNp94mopRFXugURfqlkcyOcDyinnA8op4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813103%2Forg%2Fb2e9571d6001a4647770091fc6cd6d4a.jpeg%2F08VQczKJBgQNp94mopRFXugURfqlkcyOcDyinnA8op4&h=357db291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813095/org/849d4a724e31e87f29b8828b7694116b.jpeg/8_Boo4b3Z2bZ2LbdYJiTIl53ZYsLQSlRLetDSy3rQ0s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813095%2Forg%2F849d4a724e31e87f29b8828b7694116b.jpeg%2F8_Boo4b3Z2bZ2LbdYJiTIl53ZYsLQSlRLetDSy3rQ0s&h=e84589fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豬兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 曹曦月<br />\n<br />\n現年25歲的曹曦月，在劇中飾演蛛兒，她曾在《楚喬傳》中飾演錦燭一角，觀眾大讚她演繹出角色格複雜內心深沉的感覺。曹曦月更因為網劇《校花的貼身高手》被封為「校花代言人」，有「清純版杉菜」之稱。她私下的打扮也少女感十足，不過看她的機場Look就比較隨性，用大褸同頭髮包到自己實一實，似乎很怕被人認出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813164/org/7e887afee127402f06092adadc68d82f.jpeg/AsQxUrDAvH6DQu1e8l7LPKQSJL9aI5r-3dEsat3RLGo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813164%2Forg%2F7e887afee127402f06092adadc68d82f.jpeg%2FAsQxUrDAvH6DQu1e8l7LPKQSJL9aI5r-3dEsat3RLGo&h=cf785262&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813169/org/b2e4a33271ecfd16a8909d7731bccda6.jpg/pKcIh4Z-6YA9Rr1JCPMTQCwd3XgRHPsCw79Dr8O_Q68\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813169%2Forg%2Fb2e4a33271ecfd16a8909d7731bccda6.jpg%2FpKcIh4Z-6YA9Rr1JCPMTQCwd3XgRHPsCw79Dr8O_Q68&h=86256b06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813177/org/1d8b3eefdc4ae0fa5befd6e21aeeff6f.jpg/2rerPMCBe3HbNiEM_XzsPwMZVZZVXTP_fORhxnzkYcY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813177%2Forg%2F1d8b3eefdc4ae0fa5befd6e21aeeff6f.jpg%2F2rerPMCBe3HbNiEM_XzsPwMZVZZVXTP_fORhxnzkYcY&h=f8df6dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813167/org/a06ad8ddbf2588bbff61b75cc319b040.jpg/e0_2RxEyh1yBO0Ksx7VRLPUcHOcxf1rUosMqi6LDKos\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813167%2Forg%2Fa06ad8ddbf2588bbff61b75cc319b040.jpg%2Fe0_2RxEyh1yBO0Ksx7VRLPUcHOcxf1rUosMqi6LDKos&h=763dcd82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 陳欣予<br />\n<br />\n劇中的殷素素亦正亦邪，同時又聰明機智，不少網民大讚陳欣予樣子秀麗，十分貼合角色。雖然在她身上有不少傳聞，除了說她已婚之外，更頻頻指她整容。不過陳欣予多數素顏現身機場，似乎一點都不介意以真面目示人！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2813199/org/71b6ce6dca172223a1d2f025f89186c3.jpeg/4PKILYtc_uxJe8zmGUcW084JR446t6XmE_zb-xP82_s?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2813199%2Forg%2F71b6ce6dca172223a1d2f025f89186c3.jpeg%2F4PKILYtc_uxJe8zmGUcW084JR446t6XmE_zb-xP82_s%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6c6343b7&s=